    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>VALHALLA: OFFICERS CHARGED</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By ELSA BRENNER</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Brenner, Elsa</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Four corrections officers at County Jail in Valhalla, NY, are suspended and charged with making fraudulent disability claims (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Four correction officers have been charged with making fraudulent disability claims at the County Jail in Valhalla. Authorities said three officers made false representations to their doctors about their ability to work, obtaining $46,900 in disability benefits. A fourth is accused of submitting forged doctor's notes excusing him from his duties. All four officers have been suspended.</p>
        <p>ELSA BRENNER</p>
      </block>
